central united states on tuesday temperatures topped 100 degrees 
in some states 
showers and thunderstorms fell mainly over the southeast from 
florida and southern georgia to southeastern louisiana 
in jacksonville fla thunderstorms dropped an inch of rain in 
the six hours ending at 2 pm edt 
