barry 54 is facing 10 misdemeanor cocaine possession charges 
one misdemeanor cocaine conspiracy charge and three felony counts 
of lying to a grand jury about his alleged drug use 
moore has said the two used drugs together more than 100 times 
between 1986 and 1988 
moore also recanted earlier testimony that she had violated fbi 
