hotel and that he brought up the subject of drugs the minute he 
walked in her hotel room 
is it still your testimony that you went beyond your 
instructions asked retchin 
no its not said moore 
mundy attacking moores motives and credibility said she has 
received more than 32000 in aid from the government but that 
allowed moore under later prosecution questioning to tell jurors 
she was in the justice departments witness protection program 
because the government contends it has evidence a 100000 contract 
has been put out on her life 
the jury was told that barry had nothing to do with that threat 
against moores life 
and retchin countering mundys suggestion that barry was merely 
led along by moore asked her in a series of questions whether she 
helped barry use crack cocaine during the sting 
no i did not moore said 
