it was very tense very emotional a lot of yelling and 
screaming 
vento was the trial defendant to be tried in the attack five 
other brooklyn youths face trial in the case 
joseph fama 19 identified by vento as the triggerman was 
convicted of murder in the first trial and sentenced to 32 and 
twothirds years to life keith mondello 19 received five and 
onethird to 16 years for his convictions on lesser charges 
