is it at the level of armenia no but was armenia at the 
level of mexico no was mexico at the level of san francisco 
no cassell said if the story gets buried the contributions 
subside 
the san francisco quake occurred while millions were watching 
the 1989 world series on national television for days it was 
featured prominently in the nations newspapers the armenian quake 
occurred during the holiday season a natural time for giving 
the iranian quake already has been knocked from page 1 by 
stories on german reunification and president bushs relaxing of 
his no new taxes stand if it was another country the news 
wouldnt be diminished as quickly sadaghiani said last week 
iranian president hashemi rafsanjani on monday thanked 98 
countries for assistance but left out the united states which the 
state department says has given 760000 in aid from government and 
private sources he also ignored relief efforts by iraq and saudi 
arabia 
its unfortunate that people dont forget these things during 
times of disaster but human beings are vengeful he said 
iranians stormed the us embassy in tehran in november 1979 
and held 52 americans for 444 days also american officials blamed 
irans late religious leader ayatollah khomeini for morerecent 
terrorism and hostagetaking 
the united states has not settled its accounts with iran 
austin said it will be a while before people feel like 
establishing any kind of normal relationship with iran 
at the penn state donation booths which will be open until the 
independence day break americans and foreigners were giving but 
